Pages
=====

== About

  ContentEditor is a MiniCMS like for Altered Beast (could work with Beast too).
  It allows creation of simple content pages.

== Install

1. script/runner 'Beast::Plugins::ContentEditor.install'

2. install Rails Plugin beast_plugins:

  script/plugin http://svn.techno-weenie.net/projects/beast/plugins/beast_plugins/

3. skip to 4 if you have config/initializers/plugins.rb

  3.1. create config/initializers/plugins.rb

  3.2. add:

    Beast::Plugin.initialize_plugins 'Beast::Plugins::ContentEditor'

  3.3 [esc]:wq!

  3.4. done.

4. append:

    'Beast::Plugins::ContentEditor'

   to the list of plugins 

   done.

